00:59:46,774 --> 00:59:48,234
that just stays at the center.

1507
00:59:48,614 --> 00:59:50,814
The point on the hyperboloid over here,

1508
00:59:54,814 --> 00:59:55,674
I don't know,

1509
00:59:55,674 --> 00:59:57,494
intersects somewheres over here.

