how far out on this plane do you go?

1515
01:00:10,314 --> 01:00:12,574
As you move out on the hyperboloid,

1516
01:00:13,274 --> 01:00:15,324
you get closer and closer to

1517
01:00:15,324 --> 01:00:17,374
the asymptotes of the hyperboloid here,

1518
