01:00:27,194 --> 01:00:32,194
So no point is ever mapped out beyond this circle.

1522
01:00:33,134 --> 01:00:36,034
Even the asymptotically far away points,

1523
01:00:36,334 --> 01:00:36,874
very,

1524
01:00:36,874 --> 01:00:37,694
very far away,

1525
01:00:38,393 --> 01:00:40,994
simply map the points near the boundary,

1526
01:00:41,274 --> 01:00:43,134
near the circle here.

1527
01:00:44,194 --> 01:00:45,454
So in doing this mapping,

1528
01:00:45,454 --> 01:00:46,014
again,

1529
01:00:47,074 --> 01:00:50,514
every point winds up in a particular place.

1530
01:00:51,174 --> 01:00:51,994
That's good.

